Absolute duties: 
Duty 1 - Do not interfere with others people autonomous choices, even if they are self-distructive or irrational. 

Prima-facie duties: 
Duty 2 - Help people exert their faculty to choose, e.g. by helping them understand what they want or putting them in the 
position to choose. 
!Exception to duty 2: ...Unless this conflicts with your own autonomous choice!
